         <abstract id="aspace_62e5ce97f18739f5bc5635e97c98a489">The collection contains photographs and recordings of conferences and presentations, articles and publications on gays and gays in health care, and of newsletters, mailings, and fliers.  Also included are the working papers of the Gay Nurse Alliance, an advocacy group for gay patients and nurses and an education disseminator for health care professionals and others.</abstract>
      </did>
