      <scopecontent id="aspace_e4872804b78e9d79373abb95e6467a56">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The bulk consists of photographs and recordings of conferences and presentations, articles and publications on gays and gays in health care, and of newsletters, mailings, and fliers. There are some manuscripts, correspondence, and other publicity material from GNA and other organizations, including GNA's <title>Signal</title> newsletter. Also includes buttons and badges from conferences.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
